The mural with Mindaro depicts them presenting several charms, directly hinting towards the charms needed for each pedestal at Mindaro's Shrine
===Mindaro's Respite===
[[File:Sketchu Spring Mindaro Completed.webp|thumb|none|Completed Mindaro's Shrine, leading to Mindaro's Respite.]]
Upon completing the shrine, a portal will open behind the pedestals leading to Mindaro's Respite, completing the shrine will make it appear for all users in the instance.
{{Spoiler|
[[File:Sketchu Spring Mindaro Secret.webp|thumb|The main chamber.]]Mindaro's Respite contains a couple avatars along with murals. A secret code for the portal on the wall in the main chamber. Interacting with the orb in the main chamber will transform The Spring's surroundings into a grassland.